%%{ init: { 'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': { 'primaryColor': '#f59e0b', 'primaryBorderColor': '#d97706', 'primaryTextColor': '#fefce8', 'lineColor': '#78716c', 'secondaryColor': '#1c1410', 'tertiaryColor': '#231a10', 'noteBkgColor': '#292524', 'noteTextColor': '#fef3c7', 'noteBorderColor': '#78716c' } } }%%

sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Lead as Lead Agent<br/>(Architecture)
    participant Alpha as Alpha Agent<br/>(Code + Logic)
    participant Bravo as Bravo Agent<br/>(Visual + Functional)
    participant Gate as Consensus Gate

    Note over Orch,Gate: Phase N implementation complete -- gate check begins

    Orch->>Lead: Checkpoint prompt (independent)
    Orch->>Alpha: Checkpoint prompt (independent)
    Orch->>Bravo: Checkpoint prompt (independent)

    Note over Lead,Bravo: Zero shared context -- each agent starts fresh

    par Lead validates
        Lead->>Lead: Cross-component consistency
        Lead->>Lead: Pattern compliance audit
        Lead->>Lead: SDK + CLI path check
    and Alpha validates
        Alpha->>Alpha: Line-by-line logic review
        Alpha->>Alpha: State machine analysis
        Alpha->>Alpha: Accumulation pattern check
    and Bravo validates
        Bravo->>Bravo: Exercise running system
        Bravo->>Bravo: UI behavior under real data
        Bravo->>Bravo: Edge case verification
    end

    Lead-->>Gate: VOTE: PASS + evidence artifact
    Alpha-->>Gate: VOTE: FAIL + evidence artifact
    Bravo-->>Gate: VOTE: PASS + evidence artifact

    Note over Gate: Unanimous PASS required<br/>Alpha FAIL -- gate stays CLOSED

    Gate->>Orch: BLOCKED -- Alpha found P2 bug<br/>Line 926: += causes text duplication

    Note over Orch,Gate: Fix cycle -- implement fix

    Orch->>Orch: Fix 1: message.text += to =<br/>Fix 2: preserve lastProcessedMessageIndex

    Note over Orch,Gate: Re-validation -- ALL agents re-run (no stale votes)

    Orch->>Lead: Re-validate with fix applied
    Orch->>Alpha: Re-validate with fix applied
    Orch->>Bravo: Re-validate with fix applied

    par Lead re-validates
        Lead->>Lead: Verify fix across both execution paths
    and Alpha re-validates
        Alpha->>Alpha: Confirm assignment replaces append
        Alpha->>Alpha: Confirm index preserved
    and Bravo re-validates
        Bravo->>Bravo: Run app -- renders "Four." not "Four.Four."
    end

    Lead-->>Gate: VOTE: PASS + evidence
    Alpha-->>Gate: VOTE: PASS + evidence
    Bravo-->>Gate: VOTE: PASS + evidence

    Note over Gate: 3/3 PASS -- gate OPENS

    Gate->>Orch: GATE OPEN -- advance to Phase N+1
